	<h1 class="title">「戛纳电影节」红毯之下的电影交易市场不温不火</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/102277/small/102277.jpg?1432868256" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">韩方航</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-14 13:40:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/9580/medium/9580.jpg?1436675612" alt="" />			
	</div>
