<div class="com-share" data-id="9580" data-title="《「戛纳电影节」红毯之下的电影交易市场不温不火》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/9580/medium/9580.jpg?1436675612" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/9580.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
